@tenderlove https://twitter.com/tenderlove/statuses/231807764907819008

Today I looked into adding support for the postgresql geo types. Everything went well but I didn't manage to get AR to type cast pg's string representation into an array. (See the failing `base_test.rb`)

Got a pointer for me?

It fixes #3047, #2483.

@rafaelfranca I've backported two commits, first to support jar options on all stores and second to fix issue with re-streaming of cookie jar with the same value. Also I've found that one of the tests in the second commit was wrongly written, so I've corrected that as well.

All tests pass.
